As mentioned recently CPH used to have hidden sellers at 6 & 7 previously. To have buyers at 8 on last Wednesday is amazing. This time I see power in this counter especially it close at 8 for 2 consecutive sessions n traded volume 2 sessions ago was amazingly much bigger compared to the past many months. I will expect more upward move soon to hit at least 10. Let's see...

Another potential counter to watch this coming week is Rex. Rex had been trapped in range for the past 2-3 months. Last week it finally broke out of the range. To be able to breakout of range showed power. Last Wednesday closed with an ugly inverted hammer but price didn't drop further on Thursday but instead closed with a reversal candle.
